# --- Contact form (optional) ---
# Enable real form submissions so messages arrive without opening a mail app.
#   1. Create a free form at https://formspree.io and copy its form id
#      (the part after /f/ in the endpoint, e.g. "xyzabcde").
#   2. Copy this file to .env.local and paste the id below, then rebuild.
# Without this, the contact form falls back to a prefilled mailto — which
# always works, it just opens the visitor's email app instead of sending.
VITE_FORMSPREE_ID=
